node.text: @williamsmunoz56 beautiful lady please if you don't mind I will love the both of us to be friends

31st May 2020 - #circuitbreakerday55 We've made it so far! Just finished an online lesson with @winson93ren , @jiassst and @isaacjianming to make Choux pastries! Not an easy task to keep washing and following lesson at the same time to bake these lovelies! I felt like I was broadcasting live with all the lighting and cameras I've got! Still a fun and interactive session and I've learnt new things!
.
